    <li class="f5 black-60 db mb2 tracked pt3 pb3 mr2"><span class='li mr2 w2'>&rarr;</span>
      Did you find these therapies helpful? Why?
      <br>
      <textarea class="mt3 w-80 mw7 vh-5 ba b--black-30 br3 h4" type="text" name="therapies_helpful" rows="8" cols="80" placeholder="Write here please" aria-label='please let us know your therapy was helpful'></textarea>
    </li>

    <li class="f5 black-60 db mb2 tracked pt3 pb3 mr2"><span class='li mr2 w2'>&rarr;</span>
      What helps to keep you well? (e.g friends, support from family?)
      <textarea class="mt3 w-80 mw7 vh-5 ba b--black-30 br3 h4" type="text" name="keep_well" rows="8" cols="80" placeholder="Write here please" aria-label='what helps keep you well'></textarea>
